edu.utsa.fileflow.cfg

Class FlowPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.utsa.fileflow.cfg.FlowPoint

  • public class FlowPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    A FlowPoint represents a node in the ControlFlowGraph. It can have any amount of entry points and should have zero, one or two exit points since there is no switch statements in the FileFlow grammar.
    Author:
    Rodney Rodriguez
